{
  "page": "Walrus",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>walrus</b> is a large semiaquatic mammal related to the <a href=\"/index.php/Seal\" title=\"Seal\">seal</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Range\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Range</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Culture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Culture</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Range\">Range</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walrus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Range\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Walrus colonies can be found <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Frozen_Shore\" title=\"Frozen Shore\">Frozen Shore</a> and along the northern coasts of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf836_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf836-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf838_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf838-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Many walruses are found in <a href=\"/index.php/Lorath_Bay\" title=\"Lorath Bay\">Lorath Bay</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf821_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf821-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Bay_of_Tusks\" title=\"Bay of Tusks\">Bay of Tusks</a> is well known as breeding ground for the animals.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf836_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf836-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walrus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Some <a href=\"/index.php/Men_of_the_Frozen_Shore\" title=\"Men of the Frozen Shore\">men of the Frozen Shore</a> ride chariots of walrus bones<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and wear walrus tusks on their heads,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and one of their leaders is known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Walrus\" title=\"Great Walrus\">Great Walrus</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Farwynd_of_the_Lonely_Light\" title=\"House Farwynd of the Lonely Light\">House Farwynd of the Lonely Light</a> and their <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> are rumored to be <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">skinchangers</a> who can can take the forms of walruses, <a href=\"/index.php/Spotted_whale\" title=\"Spotted whale\">spotted whales</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Sea_lion\" title=\"Sea lion\">sea lions</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf75.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf75.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Walrus tusks make up much of the trade of <a href=\"/index.php/Lorath\" title=\"Lorath\">Lorath</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf821_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf821-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walrus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In some legends from <a href=\"/index.php/Lorath\" title=\"Lorath\">Lorath</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Mazemakers\" title=\"Mazemakers\">mazemakers</a> were destroyed by <a href=\"/index.php/Walrus-men\" title=\"Walrus-men\">walrus-men</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf821_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf821-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Toad\" title=\"Lord Toad\">Lord Toad</a> described Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walderan_Tarbeck\" title=\"Walderan Tarbeck\">Walderan Tarbeck</a> as \"a wallowing walrus of a man\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walrus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walrus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gylbert_Farwynd\" title=\"Gylbert Farwynd\">Gylbert Farwynd</a> includes walrus tusks among the treasures he offers to the assembled <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a>. The captains turn away from his gifts, leaving less prestigious men to scramble after them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walrus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf836-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf836_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf836_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; Beyond the Free Cities&#32;(The Shivering Sea).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf838-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf838_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; Beyond the Free Cities&#32;(East of Ib).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf821-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf821_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf821_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf821_3-2\">3.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; The Free Cities&#32;(Lorath).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Jon II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_58\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 58\">Chapter 58</a>, Jon XII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf75.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf75.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Seven Kingdoms&#58; The Iron Islands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">8.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\">8.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 19\">Chapter 19</a>, The Drowned Man.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">georgerrmartin.com: <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.georgerrmartin.com/world-of-ice-and-fire-sample/\">The Westerlands (unabridged)</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Animals\" title=\"Template:Animals\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Animals&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Animals (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Animals&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bestiary\" title=\"Bestiary\">Animals of the known world</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Birds</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bluejay\" title=\"Bluejay\">Bluejay</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Crane\" title=\"Crane\">Crane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Crow\" title=\"Crow\">Crow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eagle\" title=\"Eagle\">Eagle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Falcon\" title=\"Falcon\">Falcon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Goose\" title=\"Goose\">Goose</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gull\" title=\"Gull\">Gull</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hawk\" title=\"Hawk\">Hawk</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Heron\" title=\"Heron\">Heron</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kite\" title=\"Kite\">Kite</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lark_(bird)\" title=\"Lark (bird)\">Lark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Magpie\" title=\"Magpie\">Magpie</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mockingbird\" title=\"Mockingbird\">Mockingbird</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nightingale\" title=\"Nightingale\">Nightingale</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Owl\" title=\"Owl\">Owl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Parrot\" title=\"Parrot\">Parrot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Peacock\" title=\"Peacock\">Peacock</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pigeon\" title=\"Pigeon\">Pigeon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Quail\" title=\"Quail\">Quail</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">Raven</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/White_raven\" title=\"White raven\">White raven</a></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rook_(bird)\" title=\"Rook (bird)\">Rook</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sandpiper\" title=\"Sandpiper\">Sandpiper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Snow_shrike\" title=\"Snow shrike\">Snow shrike</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sparrow\" title=\"Sparrow\">Sparrow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stork\" title=\"Stork\">Stork</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Swan\" title=\"Swan\">Swan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tern\" title=\"Tern\">Tern</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vulture\" title=